transforms.code:
FROM    (
            SELECT  *
            FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_role_merchant
            WHERE   dt = '20250802'
        ) a
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  *
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_involved_party_role
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                ) b
ON      a.ip_role_id = b.ip_role_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  tnt_inst_id
                            ,id
                            ,name
                            ,value
                            ,principal_id
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_common_unique_key
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    AND     name = 'MIGRATE_IP_UK'
                ) c
ON      a.ip_role_id = c.principal_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  contact_target_id
                            ,GET_JSON_OBJECT(contact_way_value,'$.mcc') AS mcc
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_cp_contact_way
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    AND     contact_way_type = '73'
                    GROUP BY contact_target_id
                             ,GET_JSON_OBJECT(contact_way_value,'$.mcc')
                ) f
ON      a.ip_role_id = f.contact_target_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  data_item_key
                            ,GET_JSON_OBJECT(serialized_content,'$.name') AS mcc_name
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cp_data_item_trunk_content
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    AND     data_item_name = 'MerchantCategoryCode'
                    GROUP BY data_item_key
                             ,GET_JSON_OBJECT(serialized_content,'$.name')
                ) d
ON      f.mcc = d.data_item_key
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  contact_target_id
                            ,REGEXP_REPLACE(ext_properties,'\\\\\"','\"') AS ext_properties
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_cp_contact_person
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    AND     contact_person_rel_type = '1'
                ) e
ON      a.ip_role_id = e.contact_target_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  ip_id
                            ,TRIM(GET_JSON_OBJECT(pronounce_name,'$.lastName')) AS pronounce_name
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cu_involved_party
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    AND     ip_type = 2
                ) g
ON      b.ip_id = g.ip_id

FROM    fund t1
LEFT OUTER JOIN mbr t2
ON      t1.merchant_id = t2.merchant_id

FROM    (
                SELECT  TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(contract_query_time),'yyyy-MM-dd') AS report_date
                        ,bill_no
                        ,product_code
                        ,bill_type
                        ,original_trans_id
                        ,CASE   WHEN bill_type = 'REFUND' THEN CAST(service_amt AS BIGINT) * (
                                            -1
                                )
                                ELSE CAST(service_amt AS BIGINT)
                        END AS service_amt
                        ,CASE   WHEN bill_type = 'REFUND' THEN CAST(bill_amt AS BIGINT) * (
                                            -1
                                )
                                ELSE CAST(bill_amt AS BIGINT)
                        END AS bill_amt
                FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_fee_main_bill_pt
                WHERE   YEAR >= '2022'
                AND     CAST(bill_amt AS BIGINT) <> 0
                AND     product_code IN ('51051000101000100051','51051000101000100048','51051000101000100047','51051000101000100053','51051000100000000110')
            ) t1
    LEFT JOIN   (
                    SELECT  bill_no
                            ,fee_item_code
                            ,fee_amt
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_fee_bill_detail_fee_pt
                    WHERE   YEAR <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4)
                    AND     CAST(fee_amt AS BIGINT) <> 0
                ) t2
    ON      t1.bill_no = t2.bill_no

FROM    service_name_agg AS fund
    INNER JOIN merchant_cat_map AS cat
    ON      fund.fund_type = cat.merchant_id
    AND     fund.service_name = cat.join_key_value

FROM    biz_name_agg AS fund
    INNER JOIN merchant_cat_map AS cat
    ON      fund.fund_type = cat.merchant_id

FROM    invoker_id_agg AS fund
    INNER JOIN merchant_cat_map AS cat
    ON      fund.fund_type = cat.merchant_id
    AND     fund.invoker_id = cat.join_key_value

FROM    (
                SELECT  COALESCE(pre_acquirement_id,a.acquirement_id) AS order_id
                        ,merchant_trans_type AS fund_type
                        ,merchant_id AS join_cat
                        ,'' AS invoker_id 
                        ,order_amt AS amount
                        ,CASE WHEN a.order_status = 'SUCCESS' AND b.acquirement_id IS NOT NULL THEN 'REFUND'
                              WHEN a.order_status = 'CLOSED' THEN 'REFUND'
                              ELSE 'SUCCESS' END AS order_status
                        ,product_code
                        ,'AQC' AS trx_type
                        ,created_time AS gmt_create
                FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_aqc_base_pt a
                LEFT JOIN (SELECT acquirement_id FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_aqc_refund_pt WHERE year >= '2024'
                           UNION ALL 
                           SELECT acquirement_id FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_aqc_fund_back WHERE dt = '20250802') b
                ON a.acquirement_id = b.acquirement_id
                WHERE   year >= '2024'
                AND order_status IN ('SUCCESS','CLOSED')
                UNION ALL
                SELECT  fund_order_id AS order_id
                        ,fund_type
                        ,fund_type AS join_cat
                        ,invoker_id
                        ,fund_amount AS amount
                        ,CASE WHEN (fund_order_status = 'SUCCESS'
                                    AND COALESCE(fund_sub_status,0) <> 'REVERSE_PAY'
                                    AND COALESCE(tracking_flag,0) <> 'REFUND_SUCCESS') THEN 'SUCCESS' ELSE 'REFUND' END AS order_status
                        ,product_code
                        ,'FUND' AS trx_type
                        ,created_time
                FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_ap_fund_order_pt
                WHERE   year >= '2024'
                AND fund_order_status IN ('SUCCESS','REFUND')
            ) t

FROM    (
                SELECT  gmt_create
                        ,gmt_exchange
                        ,origin_biz_no AS order_id
                        ,order_id AS asset_flux_id
                        ,amount
                        ,charge_amount
                FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_af_pay_order_pt
                WHERE   year >= '2024'
                AND     GET_JSON_OBJECT(order_ext,'$.includePlatformFeeAmount') IS NOT NULL
                AND     status = 'SUCCESS'
            ) pay
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                        SELECT  gmt_create
                                ,origin_biz_no AS order_id
                                ,payment_id
                                ,amount
                                ,charge_amount
                                ,GET_JSON_OBJECT(order_ext,'$.isNeedToRefundPlatformFee')
                        FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_af_refund_order_pt
                        WHERE   year >= '2024'
                        AND     GET_JSON_OBJECT(order_ext,'$.isNeedToRefundPlatformFee') = 'true'
                    ) refund
    ON      pay.asset_flux_id = refund.payment_id

FROM    (
                SELECT  merchant_id
                        ,category_level_2
                        ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY merchant_id ORDER BY majority DESC ) AS rn
                FROM    (
                            SELECT  merchant_id
                                    ,category_level_2
                                    ,COUNT(*) AS majority
                            FROM    merchant_cat_map
                            GROUP BY merchant_id
                                     ,category_level_2
                        ) 
            )

FROM    platform_fee a
    INNER JOIN aqc_fund b
    ON      a.order_id = b.order_id
    LEFT OUTER JOIN merchant_cat_map_new c
    ON      b.join_cat = c.merchant_id
    LEFT OUTER JOIN aqc_prod_code d
    ON      b.product_code = d.parameter_pd_code
